<title>Conic Sections and Quadric Surfaces</title>
<introduction>
</p>

<p>xml:id="ap_quadric"
</p>

<p>A conic section is the curve of intersection of a cone and a plane
that does not pass through the vertex of the cone.
This is illustrated in the figures below.
\vadjust{
</p>
